name: Filling void, negative bust, 2021
description:
watercolors, acrylic, digital print on old paper, coffee and collage, photoshop, cm 20x30
part of the series Filling Void, a collection of mixed media works started mid 2020 trying to investigate the opposite concepts of full and void with painting, collage and digital print, in this case the cutout of an old paper draw the silhouette of bust over an informal background.
